name: Airplane Parking! Real Plane Pilot Drive and Park - Runway Traffic Control Simulator - Full Version
name_original: Airplane Parking! Real Plane Pilot Drive and Park - Runway Traffic Control Simulator - Full Version
description:
*** GAME DOES NOT CONTAIN ADS ***

Craving for a totally new parking game challenge?!
Wait no more 'coz Airplane Parking is here!

Same parking game but this time you are driving a Jumbo Airplane!
You will be the pilot to drive the plane to the ramp.

After landing, your mission is to park your aircraft to safety.
Test your driving skills on tight corners and clear the level without hitting obstacles!
